reviewText:
I love this series.... BUT
After receiving the 1, 2 and 3 series of Outrageous Fortune I began watching them from the beginning.  Im up to Series 3 disk 2 and found that the disc is broken thats 6 episodes of this series I now have to miss. Unless I buy a new version I don't believe its up to me as I received it broken. Being addicted to this series I don't want to go ahead and continue watching disk 3 as I would have missed so much. Not Happy. Please check product BEFORE sending to receiver.
